latestIgtvVideos.title: Vegetarian Delight in Bangalore?
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hi Peeps! 
So, I spent a beautiful afternoon with some friends at a super pretty cafe @streetstoryssblr . 
This is located at Indranagar, Bangalore. 📍
Besides the pretty ambiance, go here if you want to experience a twist in the vegetarian menu. 
My favourites of the lot that I tasted definitely has to be Rajma Ghee Khichdi, Bangkok Stir Fry, Burmese Khao Suey, Texture of Eggplant and Avocado Mousse. I also liked the Orange and Lime Kafir. 
They have a vast vegetarian menu.
So go here the next time you are looking for some good vibes and vegetarian food ✨.
.
.
Also, tag a friend who you think might enjoy this video. Don’t forget to leave a comment if you like it! 🌸 .
.
